at Anthony won all of those contests.)						<br/><br />						<span class="style3">							Cinema Central, the latest, greatest feature films from Hollywood and Beyond						</span>						<br/><br />						From Hollywood in the USA to Bollywood in India to Nollywood in Nigeria, from the cinematic centers of England, France, Russia, Mexico, Australia, Israel and every major producer of feature films, the world's most happening flicks will be on view on one of Cinema Central's 22 screens.						<br/><br />						Unlike typical standalone multiplexes or mall multi-screen theater complexes with low-ceilinged, empty box-like spectator sections and mini-screens barely larger than the 100-inch HDTV common in high-end "home theaters," 21 of Cinema Central's theaters will be built in the grand style with soaring ceilings, ornamented areas for box and general admission seats, true theater-size screens, and the latest in 3D projection and multi-track, multi-dimensional Dolby and DTS sound systems.						<br/><br />						The 22nd theater? The largest IMAX screen anywhere. Next generation holographic 3D ready. 360-degree, 36-channel surround sound with speaker arrays embedded in the ceiling, floor and all sides of the acoustically superb, horseshoe-shaped seating area.					</div>				</div>			</div>			<div id="TwitterFeedHeader"></div>			<div id="TwitterFeedContainer" style="width: 380px;  padding: 0px 0px 10px 70px; height: 87px; ">			<!-- <a title="Live the M life" rel="lightbox[southchapel]" href="/peelad/interior_popup.swf?width=252&amp;height=525"><img src="images/home/Mlife-Banner.jpg" width="300" height="87" border="0" style="margin: 0px; float: left;"/></a> -->			</div>			<div class="HomePageRule"></div>			<!-- Twitter Feed -->			<div id="TwitterFeedContainer"><img src="images/btn-Twitter-on.jpg">				<span id="lblDisplayTweet_LblTweet"> 					<p>#FF #GlobalLtd @MarginInvestors @PennyStock @AcesOfACTS </p>				</span>			</div>			<!-- /Twitter Feed -->				<d